    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next great adventure. This stunning machine carries itself with the quiet confidence of a car that has been cherished, not merely owned. Every curve catches the light just so, the interior breathes that rare blend of leather and possibility, and the engine \u2014 oh, the engine \u2014 hums with a purposeful, road-hungry energy that reminds you why you fell in love with driving in the first place. She's been kept out of the rain, away from the chaos, treated like the thoroughbred she is. Slide behind the wheel and feel the difference that true care makes. Opportunities like this don't linger \u2014 discerning buyers recognize a gem when they see one.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
